<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Settings | DIPOSEAT</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-soft: #F8F9FA;
            --primary-pastel: #D4E2D4;
            /* Hijau Pastel Utama */
            --accent-blue: #D4F1F4;
            --text-dark: #2D3436;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-soft);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .settings-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Navigation */
        .btn-back {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #A0AEC0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .header-title {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .header-sub {
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* Main Card */
        .settings-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 45px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }

        .section-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #2D3436;
            /* Gold subtle */
        }

        .section-label i {
            color: inherit;
            margin-right: 12px;
        }

        /* Profile/Avatar */
        .avatar-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 45px;
        }

        .avatar-main {
            width: 110px;
            height: 110px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D4E2D4 0%, #B9D1B9 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            cursor: default;
            position: relative;
            border: 5px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        /* Inputs */
        .input-group-custom {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .label-modern {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #4A5568;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }

        .form-control-custom {
            width: 100%;
            border: 2px solid #EDF2F7;
            background: #F8FAFC;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .form-control-custom:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-pastel);
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(212, 226, 212, 0.15);
        }

        /* Button Pastel */
        .btn-save-pastel {
            background-color: var(--primary-pastel);
            color: #4A5568;
            border: none;
            padding: 18px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            width: 100%;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(212, 226, 212, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-save-pastel:hover {
            background-color: #C3D3C3;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(212, 226, 212, 0.4);
        }

        /* Info Restoran Area */
        .info-card-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .info-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 22px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
        }

        .icon-circle {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 20px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .bg-mint {
            background: #E6FFFA;
            color: #319795;
        }

        .bg-blue {
            background: #EBF8FF;
            color: #3182CE;
        }

        .info-content h6 {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .info-content p {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #718096;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="settings-container">
        <div class="mb-4">
            <a href="/admin" class="btn-back">Back</a>
            <h1 class="header-title">Konfigurasi Profil</h1>
            <p class="header-sub">Atur identitas admin untuk akses sistem DIPOSEAT</p>
        </div>

        <div class="settings-card">
            <div class="section-label">
                <i class="bi bi-person-circle me-2"></i> DATA PERSONAL ADMIN
            </div>

            <% if (messages.success && messages.success.length) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-success mb-4"><%= messages.success[0] %></div>
            <% } %>
            <% if (messages.error && messages.error.length) { %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger mb-4"><%= messages.error[0] %></div>
            <% } %>

            <form action="/admin/update-settings" method="POST">
                <div class="avatar-wrapper">
                    <div class="avatar-main">
                        <span id="txtInitial">
                            <%= (admin && admin.username) ? admin.username.charAt(0).toUpperCase() : 'A' %>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="input-group-custom">
                            <label class="label-modern">Username</label>
                            <input type="text" name="username" class="form-control-custom"
                                value="<%= admin && admin.username ? admin.username : '' %>"
                                placeholder="Masukkan username baru">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-12">
                        <div class="input-group-custom">
                            <label class="label-modern">Password</label>
                            <div style="position: relative;">
                                <input type="password" name="password" id="passField" class="form-control-custom"
                                    placeholder="Kosongkan jika tidak ingin mengubah password">
                                <i class="bi bi-eye"
                                    style="position: absolute; right: 25px; top: 18px; color: #CBD5E0; cursor: pointer;"
                                    onclick="viewPass()"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-save-pastel">Perbarui Profil</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-mint"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
                <div class="info-content">
                    <h6>Analitik Reservasi</h6>
                    <p>Data reservasi diupdate secara real-time. Pantau jam sibuk restoran Anda melalui tabel management
                        meja.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-card">
                <div class="icon-circle bg-blue"><i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill"></i></div>
                <div class="info-content">
                    <h6>Keamanan Sesi</h6>
                    <p>Sesi login admin dilindungi enkripsi. Pastikan logout setelah selesai menggunakan dashboard
                        perangkat publik.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center w-100"
            style="margin-top: 80px; margin-bottom: 20px; opacity: 0.6; text-align: center;">
            <p class="small fw-bold m-0" style="color: #4A5568; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">
                &copy; 2026 DIPOSEAT. All rights reserved.
            </p>
            <p class="small m-0" style="color: #718096; font-size: 0.75rem;">
                Handcrafted with ❤️ by Computer Engineering Undip
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function viewPass() {
            const passField = document.getElementById('passField');
            passField.type = passField.type === 'password' ? 'text' : 'password';
        }
    </script>

</body>

</html>